<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l29"><expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıcken ſüll / Nu <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>gnedıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>bedencke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
